---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Zurhaar Tools" description="About Andreas Zurhaar — software engineer building tools to save you time.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">About</h1>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Hi, I'm Andreas Zurhaar — a software engineer based in the Netherlands. I build tools that automate repetitive tasks and save people time.
        </p>

        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Zurhaar Tools is my growing catalog of browser extensions, scripts, and digital products. Each tool is designed to solve a specific problem — no bloat, no subscriptions you don't need, just tools that work.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold pt-4">What I build</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Browser extensions</strong> — Chrome extensions that work while you browse.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Scripts & tools</strong> — Automation scripts and utilities that handle tedious work.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Templates & resources</strong> — Ready-to-use prompt packs, Notion templates, and more.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold pt-4">Get in touch</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Have a question or suggestion? Reach out at
          <a href="mailto:andreas@zurhaartools.com" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">andreas@zurhaartools.com</a>
          or find me on
          <a href="https://github.com/andreaszurhaar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
